{"title":"贫农老倔叔","authors":["木青"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":12,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农老倔叔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老倔叔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷起狗皮帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掖掖大棉袄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把张红纸揣怀里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑布带子紧紧腰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹭，蹭，蹭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上了道！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要往常，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们定要跟他逗逗笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可今儿个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧爹脸板着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都自动往后“稍”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有孩子娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在门口翘脚瞧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老倔叔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不看家家屋顶炊烟绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不看户户房檐“包米吊儿”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是一门走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可翻滚着浪潮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他又想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十多年走过的道儿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大颗儿的泪珠子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噗噗往下掉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他来到山脚跟儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把祖坟瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑咚跪在地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心如刀子搅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“爷爷，爹爹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们可听见儿孙叫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩儿入党啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现去参加头次支部会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀里揣着咱家史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血泪的话儿要往外掏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱这三代人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到我这儿才娶亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷把爹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拣在洋沟旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹爹把我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拣在死人坑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到头来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们又被地主逼丧命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这阶级的大仇大恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩儿牢牢刻在心！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今的幸福啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全是党的恩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就到啥时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不忘咱穷根！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看我年老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可有浑身劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱拿出整个心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老倔叔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦擦泪眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩开膀子、迈开步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老支书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在门前等！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}